---
title: Black Bean and Farro Salad with Apple, Avocado, and Radish
description: When farro and black beans join forces, the result is a protein-packed force to be reckoned with. Our chefs round out this delicious, healthy, and simple meatless dinner with creamy avocado, crisp apples, and crunchy radishes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-bean-and-farro-salad-2135c47f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/black-bean-and-farro-salad-db1f46cb.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/black-bean-and-farro-salad-57c9b64b16a866d60b8b4569
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
